name: Corneo's Bowsette TI Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for Bowsette / Princess Koopa, the fan made character created in passing in a webcomic that took the world by storm.

I retrained this to try and remove the shell and tail, which mostly worked, at least you should be able to prompt positively or negatively to add them in or out. Otherwise this isn't one of my best, but it was an interesting challenge to get a consistent look when there isn't an official version of this character.

Example images created using my 7th Heaven mix https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
